Former Soldier Hunts Arms Dealer | Search & Destroy | Action Thriller

A former soldier gets a shot at redemption against a notorious arms dealer. | A former elite soldier (Dylan Bruce) is presented with a final opportunity for redemption as he faces off against a merciless international arms dealer. Filled with incredible fight scenes, massive explosions, and relentless tension, this film stands out as one of the finest new action movies of 2025.

Enthusiasts of Jason Bourne, John Wick, and Extraction will undoubtedly appreciate this film. With Dylan Bruce at the forefront, Sergey Badyuk exuding raw intensity, and Julian Kostov portraying an unforgettable villain â€“ this is the definitive action-packed war thriller that you cannot afford to miss.

2020.  Stars: Dylan Bruce, Sergey Badyuk, Julian Kostov
